{"tid":598531,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"劣作-夜遊南生圍","createTime":"2018-03-19T14:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T16:21:13.000Z","uid":117184,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ff72aae85153d9e1c2cd25787a86dec2a16aba2b","tid":598531,"uid":117184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T14:49:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X-wrV9jqS1M&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DX-wrV9jqS1M%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=yCTaMrpfOZ6CYUu1fmQGLy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=4f7ce105\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X-wrV9jqS1M&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n歌詞:<br />\n她哼的歌聲伴著蟬聲和睦唱<br />\n漆黑中有星透著柔光閃爍<br />\n淡柔風吹心輕飄揚<br />\n這夜和她等破曉<br />\n暢談一切永不覺寂寥<br />\n笑聲不少 同鳴了心跳<br />\n<br />\n夜遊南生圍 望藍藍天際<br />\n但願拖緊這手拖一世<br />\n靜默這刻對流星起誓<br />\n站木橋一旁 相吻於湖泊<br />\n這分這秒的快樂 <br />\n榮幸有日出 做烘托<br />\n<br />\n仲打算同未來女朋友去南生圍過一晚夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2560b963b767908154661915f0d3e38bf2650f72","tid":598531,"uid":117184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T15:01:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d794f4fe186a6e81b866e0714113571ac8dbd930","tid":598531,"uid":117184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T15:33:26.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"e350717556152ad4e4223df40be7392515e197c8","tid":598531,"uid":117184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T16:40:14.000Z","msg":"有冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86b760bc35674e93ae89d22508c40c78f9dc90d","tid":598531,"uid":117184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T02:46:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b4af06e1eca27dd8089c35db6c6e934f36a04c52","tid":598531,"uid":117184,"like":0,"disl